\"run_command\"\n    ],\n    \"skill_paths\": [\n      \"frontend/accessibility.json\"\n    ]\n  },\n  {\n    \"name\": \"tester\",\n    \"role\": \"frontend_tester\",\n    \"system_prompt\": \"You are a Frontend Tester. Validate HTML, CSS, JS files. Write test_report.json with structured issues.\",\n    \"default_tools\": [\n      \"read_file\",\n      \"write_file\",\n      \"list_files\",\n      \"validate_html\",\n      \"validate_css\",\n      \"render_html_file_screenshot\",\n      \"read_image\",\n      \"run_command\"\n    ],\n    \"skill_paths\": [\n      \"tester/e2e_testing.json\"\n    ]\n  }\n]\n\n## Available Tools\nThe tool menu for this specialty:\n[\"read_file\", \"write_file\", \"list_files\", \"run_command\", \"render_html_screenshot\", \"render_html_file_screenshot\", \"validate_html\", \"validate_css\", \"read_image\", \"generate_image\"]\n\n## Task Plan\nThe planner has decomposed the task into subtasks:\n{\n  \"subtasks\": [\n    {\n      \"task_id\": \"hero-section\",\n      \"description\": \"Create a cinematic hero section with a full-width background video or high-res image of the Voltis X1 electric SUV. Include animated text overlay with the vehicle name and tagline. Output: hero.html and hero.css with smooth scroll-triggered entrance animations.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"task_id\": \"specs-section\",\n      \"description\": \"Design and implement a performance specifications section displaying key metrics (0-60 mph, top speed, horsepower, torque). Output: specs.html and specs.css using a futuristic black and silver theme with sleek iconography.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"task_id\": \"battery-safety\",\n      \"description\": \"Build two content sections: one for battery range details (range, charging time, battery capacity) and another for safety features (5-star rating, advanced driver aids). Output: battery.html, safety.html, and corresponding CSS files with consistent styling.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"task_id\": \"testimonials\",\n      \"description\": \"Develop a responsive carousel component showcasing customer testimonials with photos, names, and quotes. Output: testimonials.html and testimonials.css using smooth transitions and modern card design.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"task_id\": \"reservation-form\",\n      \"description\": \"Create a vehicle reservation form with fields for name, email, phone, preferred color, and deposit option. Include form validation and a futuristic submit button. Output: reservation.html and reservation.css.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"task_id\": \"layout-integration\",\n      \"description\": \"Assemble all sections into a single responsive landing page (index.html) with a fixed navigation bar, mobile compatibility, and consistent black/silver UI. Output: complete index.html, main.css, and integrated assets folder.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n\n## Your Job\nFor EACH subtask in the plan:\n1. Pick the BEST matching template from the available templates above\n2. Optionally EDIT the system_prompt to add task-specific details (file names, specific requirements)\n3. Select a SUBSET of tools from the available tool menu that the worker needs\n4. Set skill_paths from the template\n\n## Rules\n- Output ONLY valid JSON — no markdown fences, no extra text\n- worker_name MUST match a template name (or be \"tester\")\n- system_prompt: start from the template prompt, then add task-specific instructions\n- tool_names: only pick from the available tool menu\n- skill_paths: copy the template's skill_paths or leave empty\n\n## Output Format\n{\n  \"workers\": [\n    {\n      \"worker_name\": \"template_name\",\n      \"system_prompt\": \"Full customized system instructions for the worker\",\n      \"tool_names\": [\"tool1\", \"tool2\"],\n      \"skill_paths\": [\"path/to/skill.json\"]\n    }\n  ]\n}", "meta": {}}
